Henry O'Neill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_O%27Neill 0 Henry O'Neill (August 10, 1891 – May 18, 1961) was an American film actor known for playing gray-haired fathers, lawyers, and similarly dignified roles during the 1930s and 1940s.
